{"tid":2006211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"張崑陽：我要攬炒！","createTime":"2020-05-07T15:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T13:28:14.000Z","uid":221035,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5252c64895a5b186229266f6388ea91c2b8ea385","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:31:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">九西唔要黃碧雲！<br />\n大把選擇啦！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sunnycheungky/photos/rpp.109945333953726/135373531410906/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsunnycheungky%2Fphotos%2Frpp.109945333953726%2F135373531410906%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0IT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=3d73e70e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sunnycheungky/photos/rpp.109945333953726/135373531410906/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n內容節錄：<br />\n<br />\n//當然我們<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望泛民議員能夠爭氣</span></span></strong>，跟中共「硬着頭皮頂着幹」，扭轉局面繼續按「議事規則」守好內會，//<br />\n<br />\n//有些人仍然可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">天真地</span></span></strong>選擇判斷香港的未來還未算最壞，一切<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依然有險可守</span></span></strong>。不論泛民主派的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又傾又砌</span></span></strong>，還是當初新思維和民主思路所言的第三條出路，都是當今極權管治下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">妨礙抗爭前進的保守思維</span></span></strong>。//<br />\n<br />\n//好些人仍然<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對制度存有幻想</span></span></strong>，常談「捍衛」甚麼甚麼，其實就是抱着已經分崩離析的現有制度不肯放手。這些人都如今還在講「河水不犯井水」的一國兩制初心，講如何盡力保衛垂死的法治，卻不能直面制度的崩壞和邪惡。//<br />\n<br />\n//所以攬炒的真正意圖，就是往後的新建和重生。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攬炒現有制度確實需要勇氣，也充滿未知，但香港需要前進需要改變，時間不等人，中共的巨輪碾壓過來之前，我們要作出選擇。2020年真的是我們的攬炒時刻，政治不再是win or go home而是 win or lose home。</span></strong>//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nXNUwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nXNUwf.jpg&h=70e3fdae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f985bf9658cf119b5386c4a008d353845eb64435","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒！"},{"pid":"73b4f58d46616fe4fcb0539c4204165b074d920c","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db308ec9f4d857b2757dbd78c1c0c96a76a10ae","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"立會必投攬炒派！"},{"pid":"b910dd2f5f29cf5e587afd8851ac9b50a8eb0dd4","tid":2006211,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfa0ad5090ff9a0db82fc8dce687f2ecef4d61a","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"攬炒派is coming to town！"},{"pid":"f9d102d7ea054e92baf067f5771db3cd9dac21e8","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f894536a52123d9bbf33c0bb98858928d544f7","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb54f1751864909c51cc05b75bf759f6a46d9af4","tid":2006211,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl